《开启的封印》在日本和北美分别售出了33.8万份<ref>{{cite web|author=Fami通|title=2001年テレビゲームソフト売り上げTOP300|url=http://geimin.net/da/db/2001_ne_fa/index.php|publisher=geimin.net|accessdate=2012-07-05|language=ja|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627151515/http://geimin.net/da/db/2001_ne_fa/index.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>和74万份<ref>{{cite web|author=Edge Staff|title=The Century's Top 50 Handheld Games|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/centurys-top-50-handheld-games?page=3|publisher=Edge Online|accessdate=2012-07-05|language=en|date=2006-08-02|archive-date=2012-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120515224208/http://www.edge-online.com/features/centurys-top-50-handheld-games?page=3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的汇总得分分别为91%和90%。游戏在包括画面，音效和以精灵系统与对战模式为代表的多样玩法内，均获得了大量的好评<ref name="goodreview1">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=59181|title=Game Rankings- Golden Sun|publisher=Gamerankings.com|accessdate=2006-07-13|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060913102150/http://www.gamerankings.com/itemrankings/launchreview.asp?reviewid=59181|archive-date=2006-09-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；有些评论者认为，纵使受到了32-bit卡带的技术限制，但游戏画质依然非常高；[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]称“《开启的封印》不输给最好的[[超级任天堂|SFC]]游戏”<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web|date=2001-11-12|author=Torres, Ricardo|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensun/review.html|title=Golden Sun for GBA- gamespot.com|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2007-02-01|language=en|archive-date=2007-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070123125624/http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensun/review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而批评声主要集中在游戏过场对话过多，尤其是在序章<ref name="ignreview" />；还有批评声指称游戏走了大多数角色扮演游戏“逛地图，打随机战，战斗胜利，继续逛地图，再次打随机战……”的老套路<ref name="thunder" />。

[[G4tv.com|G4 TV]]称“这是迄今为止的最佳原创GBA角色扮演游戏”<ref name="g4">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20021213155913/http://www.techtv.com/extendedplay/reviews/story/0%2C24330%2C3373913%2C00.html |url=http://www.techtv.com/extendedplay/reviews/story/0,24330,3373913,00.html |title=''Golden Sun'' (GBA) Review |last=Concepcion |first=Miguel |date=2002-09 |work=TechTV |archivedate=2002-12-13 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，[[GamePro|GamePro]]亦评论其为“宏大的、神奇的、非常有趣的RPG，似乎它不只一个GBA游戏”<ref name="gamepro">{{cite web | url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/18240/golden-sun/ | title=''Golden Sun'' | last=Molloy | first=Sean | work=[[GamePro|GamePro]] | date=2001-11-14 | accessdate=2010-11-09 | language=en | archive-date=2009-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417023530/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/18240/golden-sun/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》称游戏为“视觉大餐”，并称其画面“会令超級任天堂玩家感到震惊”。评论家注意到游戏和之前的日式RPG相似，因而相信游戏能“轻而易举的夺得最佳原创GBA角色扮演游戏”，并成为“GBA角色扮演王国的新典范”<ref name="gireview">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050311172208/http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200201/R03.0731.1805.25876.htm?CS_pid=160111 |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200201/R03.0731.1805.25876.htm?CS_pid=160111 |title=GBA's Golden Child |author=Leeper, Justin; McNamara, Andy |work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |archivedate=2005-03-11 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《Advance》把《开启的封印》和[[神奇寶貝遊戲列表|口袋妖怪系列]]做了比较，并认为游戏画面“一饱眼福”，声音“如电影一般令人震撼”，虽然杂志谈到了游戏剧情“很陈词滥调”的毛病，但依然称游戏为“有史以来最好的掌机角色扮演游戏”<ref name="advance">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030130183329/http://gamesradar.msn.co.uk/reviews/default.asp?subsectionid=170&articleid=63489&pagetype=2 |url=http://gamesradar.msn.co.uk/reviews/default.asp?subsectionid=170&articleid=63489&pagetype=2 |title=''Golden Sun'' |last=Moulton |first=Rick |work=Advance |date=2002-05-15 |archivedate=2003-01-30 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

在2001年，《开启的封印》获得[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量奖]]之年度最佳Game Boy Advance游戏。游戏亦排到IGN读者票选游戏前100的第94位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/091-100.html|title=IGN Rankings|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2006-10-10|language=en|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/64xLORA8g?url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/091-100.html|archive-date=2012-01-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2007年，GBA寿终正寝之时，游戏获得IGN最佳Game Boy Advance游戏排名的第24名<ref name="24th">{{cite web|author=Craig Harris|date=2006|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/772/772284p1.html|title=Top 25 Game Boy Advance Games of All Time|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2007-03-18|language=en|archive-date=2012-08-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69uHox7Ko?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/772/772284p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；因为“惊人的视觉和音效，以及至少30小时的通关时间”，该网站也将黄金太阳系列评为2003年4月的月度游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/400/400522p1.html|title=IGN:Game of the Month|publisher=IGN|date=2003-04-14|accessdate=2008-07-13|language=en|archive-date=2012-09-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AhbAMbYE?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/05/02/gba-game-of-the-month-april-2003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在由任天堂力量举办的全任任天堂主机游戏TOP 200中，游戏排名第31<ref name="NP Top 200">{{Cite news|year=2006-02|title=NP Top 200|periodical=Nintendo Power|volume=200|pages=58–66|language=en}}</ref>。{{clear}}

